        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "But he said, Yea rather, blessed are they that hear the Word of God, and keep it",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". As was invariably his practice, he declines to enter into any discussion respecting the peculiar blessedness which earthly relationship to him might bring. It was not for public discussion. The Lord, in his reply, tells her? however, that there was something even more blessed than that earthly relationship to which she was alluding, and to that something all, if they pleased, might attain. Luke 11:28",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
